catchStrategyAndWeakness.weaknesses: Suzaku is weak to Water element Pals.

description: Suzaku Aqua is a Water Element Pal with the Wings of Water Partner Skill. It can be found in the desert area of Palworld, and it's weak to Electric element Pals.

partnerSkill.name: Wings of Water
partnerSkill.description: Can be ridden as a flying mount. Enhances Water attacks while mounted.

activeSkills.name: Ice Missile
activeSkills.description: Creates ice lances in the air that fly towards enemies.

activeSkills.name: Aqua Gun
activeSkills.description: Hurls a ball of water straight at an enemy.

activeSkills.name: Hydro Jet
activeSkills.description: Hurls a high-speed ball of water at an enemy.

activeSkills.name: Ignis Blast
activeSkills.description: Hurls a ball of fire straight at an enemy.

activeSkills.name: Cryst Breath
activeSkills.description: Enshrouds an enemy in a frigid blast of air, dealing continuous damage.

activeSkills.name: Aqua Burst
activeSkills.description: Creates a giant ball of water and hurls it at an enemy.

activeSkills.name: Blizzard Spike
activeSkills.description: Creates a giant lump of ice and hurls it at any enemy. It deals damage to those in the surrounding area upon impact.

location.description: Suzaku Aqua can be found in the desert area of Palworld.

catchStrategyAndWeakness.strategy: Bring an Electric Type Pal. Since Suzaku Aqua is weak to Electric element Pals, it's best to bring Electric type Pals to fight against it.
catchStrategyAndWeakness.weaknesses: Suzaku Aqua is weak to Electric element Pals.
